l:dependency.name: Amazon Web Services SDK :: Minimal
l:dependency.l:description: This plugin provides AWS SDK for Java for other plugins.

l:dependency.name: Joda-Time
l:dependency.l:description: Date and time library to replace JDK date handling

l:dependency.name: JMES Path Query library
l:dependency.l:description: Implementation of the JMES Path JSON Query langauge for Java.

l:dependency.name: AWS Java SDK for AWS KMS
l:dependency.l:description: The AWS Java SDK for AWS KMS module holds the client classes that are used for communicating with AWS Key Management Service

l:dependency.name: AWS Java SDK for AWS STS
l:dependency.l:description: The AWS Java SDK for AWS STS module holds the client classes that are used for communicating with AWS Security Token Service

l:dependency.name: software.amazon.ion:ion-java
l:dependency.l:description: A Java implementation of the Amazon Ion data notation.

l:dependency.name: AWS SDK for Java - Core
l:dependency.l:description: The AWS SDK for Java - Core module holds the classes that are used by the individual service clients to interact with Amazon Web Services. Users need to depend on aws-java-sdk artifact for accessing individual client classes.

l:dependency.name: AWS Java SDK for Amazon S3
l:dependency.l:description: The AWS Java SDK for Amazon S3 module holds the client classes that are used for communicating with Amazon Simple Storage Service
